sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.meal_number, '"'||v0.compartment||'"', '"'||v1.meal_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.airport_code||'"', '"'||v3.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v3.city_name||'"', '"'||v4.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.city_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_name||'"', '"'||v6.days_code||'"',
 '"'||v6.day_name||'"', '"'||v1.flight_id||'"' FROM food_service v0,
 flight v1, airport_service v2, city v3,
 airport_service v4, city v5, days v6 
WHERE ((v0.meal_code = ANY v1.meal_code) 
AND (((v1.from_airport = ANY v2.airport_code) 
AND ((v2.city_code = ANY v3.city_code) AND (v3.city_name = 'DENVER'))) 
AND (((v1.to_airport = ANY v4.airport_code) 
AND ((v4.city_code = ANY v5.city_code) AND (v5.city_name = 'DALLAS'))) 
AND (((v1.flight_days = ANY v6.days_code) AND (v6.day_name = 'MONDAY')) OR (((v1.flight_days = ANY v6.days_code) 
AND (v6.day_name = 'TUESDAY')) OR (((v1.flight_days = ANY v6.days_code) 
AND (v6.day_name = 'WEDNESDAY')) OR (((v1.flight_days = ANY v6.days_code) 
AND (v6.day_name = 'THURSDAY')) OR ((v1.flight_days = ANY v6.days_code) 
AND (v6.day_name = 'FRIDAY')))))))));
